<p><strong>Will my inbox be full of spam?</strong></p>
<p>I find that when I give my email out, I am only submitting it to brands I would like to be contacted by. They usually give their followers first crack at the samples and sweepstakes. If you are concerned about giving out your email I would suggest that you create an address that you will use exclusively for sweepstakes, coupon-ing, samples etc. Also remember to look for the boxes that say 'please click here if you would prefer not to receive the latest offers'.</p>
<p><strong>I clicked on a free sample link and it's taking me to a different offer / error page, why?</strong></p>
<p>If the brand's site is experiencing technical difficulties, you may be directed to an error message. We do our very best to re-direct you to a similar freebie. In the case that you get a blank page, feel free to post a comment letting us know or try again later.</p>
